+ Reaction Icons? Reaction Icons!

> I was VERY bored, so I decided to make a couple of cute little reaction images for Jay Everwood. I don't know if anyone will use these, but they're fun, and they could be like... Discord stickers? I don't know! Have fun!!!
> These were created mostly as a gift to [[*user Uncle Nicolini]], since I know you love this character. I hope I did them justice. :) Sorry if you don't like them, I know it's kind of silly!
> If anyone likes these - I have an [*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dr-vikki-lost Author Page!] Go check it out :)
